item.dc:creator: @hadlich4 hadlich4
item.description:
@hadlich4 wrote:

well the only ones that i borrowed parts from are the black dragon platebody at the bottom and the frost dragon platebody(the wings and the tail our from a cape and something else) but everything else was made fully from me and the designer. but how could you help what do you mean?

And I’ll post wireframes tomorrow, my technique was simply taking my designers drawings and outlining them then making lines and shiz so I could add spikes and different depths were they we’re needed then just cloning the whole thing and matching it up together, I think I did fairly good from learning all from YouTube/google I’ve had no schooling, although I do wanna get into graphic design as a career but I know I got a long ways to go
